&lt;li&gt;Write production code across our stack: TypeScript, JavaScript (ES6/React), Python (Django), Node.js, PostgreSQL, OpenSearch, and AWS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as Alloy&#39;s credible technical voice with customer engineering leadership, making architectural calls in real time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the engineering track of QBRs for your accounts and serve in their on-call escalation path.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Turn your work into reusable platform primitives and docs, so each deployment makes the next one faster.&lt;/li&gt;
